{"metadata":{"name":"Sunan Ibn Majah","section":{"2":{"eng-name":"The Book of the Prayer","ara-name":"كتاب الصلاة"}},"section_detail":{"2":{"hadithnumber_first":667,"hadithnumber_last":705,"arabicnumber_first":667,"arabicnumber_last":705}}},"hadiths":[{"hadithnumber":674,"arabicnumber":674,"text":"حدثنا محمد بن بشار، حدثنا يحيى بن سعيد، عن عوف بن ابي جميلة، عن سيار بن سلامة، عن ابي برزة الاسلمي، قال كان النبي صلى الله عليه وسلم يصلي صلاة الهجير التي تدعونها الظهر اذا دحضت الشمس","grades":[{"name":"Al-Albani","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Muhammad Fouad Abd al-Baqi","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Shuaib Al Arnaut","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Zubair Ali Zai","grade":"Sahih - Bukhari And Muslim"}],"reference":{"book":2,"hadith":8},"chapter":{"id":3,"ara-name":"باب وَقْتِ صَلاَةِ الظُّهْرِ ","eng-name":"The Time Of The Zuhr Prayer","isFirstHadith":false}}]}